residential.description:
Defined by its contemporary and architecturally designed, superb appointments to impressive dual level layout, this extraordinary brand-new and luxurious residence is an idyllic family retreat. Located to commanding position on the high side with bird's eye view, it is only footsteps to buses, parks and schools.
• Four great size bedrooms include substantial master bedroom with walk-in wardrobe and sizeable en-suite plus balcony with panorama view. Other three bedrooms fitted with built-in robs. • Modern open plan Kitchen fitted with stainless steel oven and gas cooktop, dishwasher and walk-in pantry. • Bright open lounge and dining area. • Luxurious fully tiled main bathroom with separate bathtub and shower area. • Home office/study area enclosed with extra storage. • Single lock-up garage with internal access. • Ducted air-conditioning. • Security features, including intercom and alarm. • Good size alfresco for the family entertainment and low maintenance backyard. With all of the above features, this magnificent family home will most certainly be suitable for all families/investors who are looking to live the life of modern, convenience and peaceful living. Be quick because this excellent opportunity will not last long. With owner determined to SELL- WILL CONSIDER OFFERS BEFORE AUCTION, please contact your exclusive agent Jitender Singh (Jeet) 0410 567 777 and Atul Bhanushali on 0402 961 515.
